A '''<tt>%use</tt>''' directive adds a [[constraint domain]] to the current Twelf [[signature]]. 

Like some other directives, for instance <tt>[[%clause]]</tt>, it is incompatible with Twelf's ability to verify [[totality assertions]] and [[metatheorems]].

